## parser

```elixir
defmodule RowParser do
  def parse(input) do
   input
    |> String.split("\n", trim: true)
    |> Stream.map(&String.trim_leading/1)
    |> Stream.map(fn str -> 
      str
      |> String.split()
      |> Enum.map(&String.to_integer/1)
    end)
    |> Enum.to_list()
  end
end

RowParser.parse(test_input)
```

